SubtitlesText.LocalizedString: You got room for one more?
Kinda takes you back doesn’t it.
Have I got a surprise for you!
Your reputation preceeds you Mr. Redfield.
Stay sharp, God only knows what's down here…
I hate playing other people's games.
Hold that thought, it's my turn.
Wanna play, huh? Alright, ready or not, here I come.
Time to save the day again.
I guess I could spare a few more minutes for you.
Leon! So, you've been caught up in this too. Hope you have the stomach for it…
Can't stay out of trouble, can you Leon.
Nice to see the cavalry's here!
It's like a Racoon City reunion.
Want me to treat your wounds?
It's gonna be a tough road.
Claire! It's so nice to see you.
You're stuck with me to the end.
Compared to Raccoon City, this is a walk in the park, right?
Why do I always feel like I'm trapped inside of a monster movie.
It's my job to make sure we all get through this alive!
No one gets left behind, not on my watch.
I've had enough of these stupid games!
Jill, I'm sorry I made you wait!
I'm getting you out of here!
We're both walking out of here!
All right, you know the drill!
I'll see you on the outside!
Alright, keep your head screwed on.
You're gonna be okay, I promise.
Come on... This shit better work!
Ok, now the fun shit begins.
Do you actually think you can defeat me?
You disappoint me. Is that the best you've got?
Too bad you won’t make it much further.
You've really become quite an inconvenience for me.
Seven minutes is all I can spare to play with you.
I tire of wasting my time with you.
You will not live to see the dawn!
I expected more of a challenge.
Your feeble attempts only delay the inevitable.
Are you trying to make me angry?
